kubelet process is running on each node 
master and worker nodes
Master Node:- 
i) API Server :- Entrypoint to K8S cluster
ii) Controller manager :-  Keeps track of whats happening in the cluster 
iii) Scheduler :- Ensure pods placement
iv)etcd:- Kubernetes backing store (Cluster brain) key value store
