API server get requests in yaml and json format
Declarative 
Is==should state 
Controller manager checkes :- Desired and actual state 
Virtual Network :- Each pod gets own ip address

Service :- Permanent IP address with dns , load balancer

Ingress:- routes traffics into cluster , Load balancer 

Configmap :- External configuration of application 
Secret :- Used to store credential data base64 encoded
